premise_source_doc_sentence: Olwen Catherine Kelly is an Irish model and actress .
She appeared in 2016 horror film The Autopsy of Jane Doe as the body of an unidentified woman Jane Doe .
It stars Emile Hirsch and Brian Cox as father-and-son coroners who experience supernatural phenomena while examining the body of an unidentified woman  (  played by Olwen Kelly  )  .
The name `` Olwen '' reappears in the folktale Einion and Olwen , about a sheep herder who travels to the Otherworld to marry Olwen .
In the Middle Welsh prose tale Culhwch ac Olwen , he is named as a member of Arthur 's retinue and takes part in the quest to win the hand of Olwen for Arthur 's cousin , Culhwch .
She was renamed RFA Olwen in 1937 and was sold in 1947 .
RFA Olwen was an oiler launched in 1917 as RFA British Light .
